{"tid":693441,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"胃炎可以點斷尾？","createTime":"2018-06-07T12:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T01:40:12.000Z","uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81001818ae0b9280702b41e833562177fa7f5a0c","tid":693441,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"照過冇幽門螺旋菌，只係淺性胃炎，而家日日噯氣、胃壁間唔中聽到沙沙聲。<br />\n<br />\n中西醫都睇過吓都唔太得，政府專科話我依啲係功能性胃病，冇得搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔太嚴重亦冇惡化，但有冇人可以幫吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524e28bd3d85d9faccbe367e732d3ca21c212b5c","tid":693441,"uid":183030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"如改變唔到生活習慣<br />\n就只有食藥，一唔舒服就食。"},{"pid":"4226eabd349a891c8c4577c5ea757aaccb7dfb31","tid":693441,"uid":8086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"唔好食有麩質既野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5815201ebec6ff70c73231b0d8fc262e8d670a","tid":693441,"uid":55593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:39:59.000Z","msg":"有乜病徵?"},{"pid":"e4dca88de32c18bc00c0a46ee4488db066c3a4ea","tid":693441,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81001818ae0b9280702b41e833562177fa7f5a0c","tid":693441,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"照過冇幽門螺旋菌，只係淺性胃炎，而家日日噯氣、胃壁間唔中聽到沙沙聲。<br />\n<br />\n中西醫都睇過吓都唔太得，政府專科話我依啲係功能性胃病，冇得搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔太嚴重亦冇惡化，但有冇人可以幫吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"胃沙沙聲？定係水聲？"},{"pid":"9bf34dca6edc3113bf48db07d8a94d4a9ace1c46","tid":693441,"uid":129509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"要幾年"},{"pid":"508d7f7e3b4b679a1cf42dffaa2954073cd4d358","tid":693441,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"日日去譚仔食大辣"},{"pid":"c9fab0390edecbe8ef4ed862a3e375928dbb1dc8","tid":693441,"uid":185142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"我一唔定時食野會胃頂住頂住<br />\n<br />\n3月第一次比人話胃炎，1個月之後開始正常返，之後間唔中復發頂住頂住，仲成日all 爛屎，間唔中先有一條<br />\n<br />\n利申:乜都冇照過，唔肚痛，只係胃頂住頂住"},{"pid":"0ef1887cdb2b1719e7fb5ed5e26abe2c069d1791","tid":693441,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"其實胃同大便爛好有關係<br />\n傳統中醫角度而言，胃就係運化既中樞，當胃運化差，就好易有停飲 ，水向下流，可以引起小便量多，如果小便少，就會大便偏軟/爛"},{"pid":"81dfb8a4233222ffcce60ffd0db7ff66d694c9b7","tid":693441,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:40:12.000Z","msg":"推吓舊 post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}